long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An essential tool for finding the best keywords to target for organic search rankings.

The MoneyWord Matrix Keyword Tool adds an additional layer of information to SEM Rush and UberSuggest keyword data by helping you easily identify keywords with high search volume and low competition. In other words, keywords that are easy to rank for and will bring lots of free, organic traffic back to your website.

Each keyword is color-coded and scored as either Poor, Fair, Good, Excellent or Jackpot. With this information at hand, you'll have a truly 'fail-proof' method for easily finding the best keywords in your niche.
